headline: LA CorpGov Forum Sept 4: Featuring Sports, Entertainment, IPOs, VCs, Activism & Asia
summary: CorpGov will launch the inaugural LA CorpGov Forum on Thursday, September 4, 2025, at 1500 N El Centro Ave, Los Angeles, California, in the heart of Hollywood. The forum will start at 2:00pm featuring an afternoon of panels and networking.
